msg: DERBY-3786: Assert failure in CacheEntry.unkeepForRemove when running stress.multi

author: kahatlen
msg: Make sure that the nested transaction used to recompile meta-data
queries does not wait for locks to prevent hangs when there's a lock
conflict between the nested transaction and the user transaction.
